rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0001
rows.name: Gosh, am I dying for some Stralu...

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I could eat it all day and
never get sick of it!

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0003
rows.name:
My favorite's the kind
with roast Urus in it.

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But you'd be fool to try and take one
down at this time of year. They're
extremely protective of their young.

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0005
rows.name:
But it's because it's so
rare to come by that I'm
so desperate for some!

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Really?! You'll help a
greedy swine like me?

rows.label: tlk44300183_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Well! I'll pay you handsomely
for this. Happy hunting!
